rComments: He is very good at explaining the course material. Focuses on theory rather than examples but if you understand what he says and pay attention during class you will be able to solve examples pretty easily without having to practice them before.
He was amazing teaching ACT245. This course was super mind opening for me. He's really helpful if you go to him and in class questions are always welcomed. I'd take it again if I could.
teaches better than the prof who taught vicki but lacks examples in class, likes to throw tricky questions on tests.
